parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the intake manifold gasket can cause coolant leakage, engine overheating, and damage to the engine, leading to costly repairs and potential safety hazards.
The failure of the head gasket can cause coolant leakage, engine overheating, and damage to the engine, leading to costly repairs and potential safety hazards.
The failure of the air conditioner compressor can cause the loss of air conditioning, which can lead to discomfort and potential safety hazards, especially in hot weather.
Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, injuries, or strandings.
symptoms: or fails to engage; the vehicle rolls backward or forward on an incline; the transmission makes a scraping noise; the engine disengages and free wheels when braking; the transmission takes time to re-engage when accelerating; metal debris is found in the transmission pan.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignition switch failure can cause the vehicle to move unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The key can be removed in any position
including while the engine is running; the vehicle moves unexpectedly
such as backing into a wall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Headlight water ingress can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: causing them to malfunction or fail; water enters the vehicle's interior
including the dashboard and instrument panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system issues can cause various malfunctions, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle's lights flicker or fail; the passenger power door lock
or slider door malfunctions; a bad odor is present in the vents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause various safety issues, including loss of critical vehicle functions, increased risk of accidents, and even fires.
symptoms: Intermittent or complete failure of various electrical systems
and alarm system. Some complaints also reported issues with the instrument panel
including illumination of warning lights and malfunctioning gauges.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag system failures can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Illumination of airbag warning lights on the instrument panel
failure of airbag system to deploy in an accident
and malfunctioning of related systems such as the check valve pin.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake system failures can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: and intermittent or complete loss of braking function.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fire Risk Due to Electrical System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause fires, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Reports of fires or smoke emanating from the vehicle
often accompanied by electrical system malfunctions.
